  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-provider support (GitHub, NPM, Docker Hub, Python)",
    "Custom package lists with grouping",
    "Real-time configuration updates via hot-reloading",
    "Multi-layer caching (L1 memory + L2 file)",
    "Hash-based security for pre-configured packages",
    "Self-hosted with Docker deployment"
